              <p>Research Medical Institute, LLC (RMI) is a clinical research organization committed to conducting high-quality observational and interventional studies in mental health and behavioral health. Our mission is to expand knowledge in psychiatric disorders, develop innovative behavioral health interventions, and improve outcomes for individuals with mental health challenges.</p>
